## Product Overview

This documentation directory covers the administrative functionality of a software platform that provides enterprise-level user management capabilities. The system includes comprehensive account management, billing and usage tracking, and Single Sign-On (SSO) authentication services.

## Product Relationships and Features

The administrative system is organized around three core functional areas:

**Account Management** serves as the central hub for user administration, providing tools and interfaces for managing user accounts, permissions, and organizational structures within the platform.

**Billing and Use** handles the commercial aspects of the platform, tracking resource consumption, managing subscription plans, and providing usage analytics and billing information to administrators.

**Single Sign-On** provides enterprise authentication capabilities, allowing organizations to integrate the platform with their existing identity management systems and streamline user access across multiple applications.

